//! Replay of frozen stake-query RPC handler vectors generated by an
//! in-package dump test running inside dcrd's internal/rpcserver
//! package at release-v2.1.5: 41 cases across estimatestakediff,
//! existsliveticket(s), getstakedifficulty, getstakeversioninfo,
//! getstakeversions, getvoteinfo, getticketpoolvalue,
//! gettreasurybalance, and livetickets, each carrying the marshalled
//! request params (parsed here through the ported dcrjson pipeline),
//! the mock chain seam facts, and the marshalled result or the exact
//! error code and message.  The block 432100 header fixture is shared
//! with the chain-query slice vectors.

